。根據圖(二)的等高線判\n     斷，甲、乙、丙三個路段需興建的項目，依序\n     為下列何者？\n     (A)橋梁-隧道-橋梁\n     (B)隧道-橋梁-隧道\n                                         圖(二)\n     (C)隧道-隧道-橋梁\n     (D)橋梁-橋梁-隧道                                      N\n"}, "is_active": false, "auto_gradable": false, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-109-society-005", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-social", "paper_id": "cap-109-society", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "圖(三)為位在臺灣北部的某工業區及其鄰近社區的         甲            乙\n分布圖，工業區排放廢氣會影響鄰近社區的空氣品                工業區\n質。若僅根據臺灣不同季節的盛行風向判斷，冬季\n時圖中哪一社區受該工業區廢氣的影響最大？            丁            丙", "options": ["甲", "乙", "丙", ""], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "16c3c9d61729", "answer_pdf_sha1": "64e8d2b7d3a1", "flags": ["needs_image", "option_incomplete"], "parse_confidence": 0.6, "original_question_number": 5, "raw_text": "5.   圖(三)為位在臺灣北部的某工業區及其鄰近社區的         甲            乙\n\n     分布圖，工業區排放廢氣會影響鄰近社區的空氣品                工業區\n     質。若僅根據臺灣不同季節的盛行風向判斷，冬季\n     時圖中哪一社區受該工業區廢氣的影響最大？            丁            丙\n     (A)甲     (B)乙\n     (C)丙     (D)丁                         圖(三)\n"}, "is_active": false, "auto_gradable": false, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-109-society-006", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-social", "paper_id": "cap-109-society", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "圖(四)為臺灣部分原住民族群的祭典與主\n矮靈祭\n要分布圖。若按圖片內容判斷，雅美族        甲\n豐年祭\n(達悟族)應為圖中何者？", "options": ["甲                                      丁", "乙", "丙 飛魚祭 猴祭", "丁                     乙                丙 圖(四)"], "correct_answer": 2, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "202